 </title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/5723/mouse-disappears-for-some-seconds-at-login/?answer=5724#post-id-5724</link><description>Open a terminal window and type:

    dconf write /org/gnome/settings-daemon/plugins/cursor/active false</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2015 09:48:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/5723/mouse-disappears-for-some-seconds-at-login/?answer=5724#post-id-5724</guid></item></channel></rss>